  "Description": {
    "English": "A compact extension to the Exosuit, installing an advanced yet portable <span class=\"name name-technology\">Medium Refiner</span>, accessible directly from the user's Exosuit interface.<br><br>Unit requires <span class=\"name name-fuel\">fuel</span> and is able to refine more complex recipes than the standard personal refiner unit.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "为套装准备的紧凑型配件，安装完毕后，使用者将能通过套装的操作界面直接使用一台先进的便携式<span class=\"name name-technology\">中型精炼机</span>。<br><br>该单元需要<span class=\"name name-fuel\">燃料</span>，与标准的个人精炼机单元相比能够使用更加复杂的精炼配方。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "強化套裝的小型額外套件，能安裝先進的可攜式<span class=\"name name-technology\">中型精製機</span>，可直接在使用者的強化套裝介面使用。<br><br>該裝置需要<span class=\"name name-fuel\">燃料</span>，能精製的物質比標準個人精製機更加複雜。"
  },
